'''Google航班'''是一个在线航班预订搜索服务，它可以帮助通过第三方供应商购买机票。
==历史==
2011年4月，[[美国司法部|美国司法部]]批准谷歌以7亿美元收购{{link-en|ITA Software}}。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.wired.com/epicenter/2011/04/google-ita/ |title=Feds Clear Google to Buy ITA Travel Search Company, Conditions Apply |author={{link-en|Ryan Singel}} |work=wired.com |date=2011-04-08 |accessdate=2011-09-13 |archive-date=2012-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120429155916/http://www.wired.com/epicenter/2011/04/google-ita |dead-url=no }}</ref>2011年9月13日，Google发布了Google航班。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.wired.com/epicenter/2011/09/google-travel-search-2/ |title=Google Upgrades Flight Search to the Jet Age |author={{link-en|Ryan Singel}} |work=[[连线|连线]] |date=2011-09-13 |accessdate=2011-09-13 |archive-date=2012-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120429000023/http://www.wired.com/epicenter/2011/09/google-travel-search-2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==响应==
这项服务推出後立即与[[智游网|智游网]]、{{link-en|Kayak.com}}和{{link-en|Bing}}等展開競爭。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theatlanticwire.com/technology/2011/09/google-travel-not-kayak-killer-yet/42433/ |title=Google Travel: Not a Kayak Killer, Yet |author=Rebeccas Greenfield |work=theatlanticwire.com |publisher={{link-en|Atlantic Media Company}} |date=2011-09-13 |accessdate=2011-09-13 |archive-date=2013-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603191718/http://www.theatlanticwire.com/technology/2011/09/google-travel-not-kayak-killer-yet/42433/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>不久，[[智游网|智游网]]向美国参议院反垄断、竞争政策和消费者权利小组委员会作证称，谷歌未能履行在谷歌搜索中将谷歌航班列表排在竞争对手名单之下的承诺。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/google-s-flight-search-breaks-promises-expedia-tells-congress.html |title=Google’s Flight Search Breaks Promise on ITA Deal, Expedia Says |first=Sara |last=Forden |work=bloomberg.com |date=2011-09-20 |accessdate=2011-09-23 |archive-date=2014-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140712233617/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/google-s-flight-search-breaks-promises-expedia-tells-congress.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

